data.description:
This beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is located on Johns Island in the highly desirable Whitney Lake Charleston community. Conveniently located 8 miles from downtown and 12 miles from the beach. 

At over 1700 square feet you are greeted by a spectacular open floor plan that provides a spacious living area. Outside there is a large back yard with two area porches and a detached garage. 

Other features include: stainless steel appliances, washer and dryer, new carpet, upstairs, walk in closets, and large attic storage. 

Whitney Lake is a 25-acre lake with trails that wrap around the lake, kayak/paddleboard accessible, covered dock and community fire pit. 

Applicants are required to complete a rental application.

No smoking allowed. Tenant responsible for water, electric, pest control and yard maintenance.
